name: Co Bra
description: Co Bra ($COBRA) is a community-driven meme token launched on Solana, blending humor, virality, and strong branding to create a bold on-chain identity. The project began as a meme—featuring a cobra in a bra—but quickly evolved into a movement powered by an active community and engaging content. Co Bra aims to dominate meme culture through consistent marketing, trending campaigns, and a fair, transparent token launch. With no team allocation and a focus on organic growth, $COBRA is building a fun, fearless brand that bites hard on the charts.
